{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/anthony-bourdain-dan-komik/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Anthony Bourdain: “Comics Are My First Love”","content":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dunia tengah berduka atas kematian Anthony Bourdain, seorang pembawa acara TV dan juga koki kenamaan yang populer lewat acaranya di CNN, Parts Unknown. Tak ada yang menyangka, sosok koki inspiratif ini meninggal dengan mengakhiri nyawanya sendiri. Kematian Bourdain semakin menyadarkan masyarakat bahwa orang sebaik dan sehangat Bourdain juga memiliki masalah mentalnya sendiri yang selama ini diabaikan oleh orang-orang di sekitarnya.</span></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48207\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48207\" data-attachment-id=\"48207\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anthony-bourdain-dan-komik/attachment/01-anthony-bourdain/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-anthony-bourdain\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-anthony-bourdain-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48207\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" alt=\"anthony bourdain\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-anthony-bourdain.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-anthony-bourdain-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48207\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Tafer Resorts</p></div></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tapi tahukah kamu? Selain menyebarkan pesan-pesan positif lewat masakannya, Anthony Bourdain juga sangat menggemari dunia seni? Di waktu senggangnya, Bourdain mendalami berbagai jenis kesenian seperti film dan literatur. Ia suka membuat film, esai, novel, dan bahkan komik!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bourdain sudah menggemari komik sejak usia yang masih muda. “Pada akhirnya saya adalah seorang </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">fanboy</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> yang </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">nerd</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> banget,” tutur Bourdain kepada CNN. Beberapa komik favoritnya seperti karya-karya <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Crumb\">Robert Crumb</a> juga komik terbitan EC Comics. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dua komik dengan pengaruh besar itu membuat Bourdain bermimpi menjadi seorang </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">author</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> komik. Ia bahkan mengaku kepada Jimmy Fallon, bahwa ia menyesal sempat menjual koleksi komiknya di tahun 1980-an hanya untuk membeli narkoba.</span></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48208\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48208\" data-attachment-id=\"48208\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anthony-bourdain-dan-komik/attachment/02-anthony-bourdain/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-anthony-bourdain\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-anthony-bourdain-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48208\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CNN\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-anthony-bourdain.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-anthony-bourdain-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48208\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CNN</p></div></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bourdain memang memiliki minat pada dunia komik. Namun, ia sendiri tak punya kemampuan menggambar yang bagus. Pada akhirnya, Bourdain memilih fokus ke aspek <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/siapa-bilang-penulis-nggak-bisa-sekeren-komikus-pede-aja-kali/\">penulisan komik</a>. Kemampuannya sebagai penulis memang sudah terpupuk matang sehingga tak banyak yang harus ia pelajari saat menerapkan kemampuan menulisnya ke dalam media komik.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Di tahun 2012, Bourdain siap untuk terjun ke dalam dunia komik. Menggandeng </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">co-writer</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Joel Rose, ilustrator Langdon Foss dan José Villarubia, Bourdain merilis komik <a href=\"https://www.vertigocomics.com/graphic-novels/get-jiro\">Get Jiro</a> lewat label Vertigo milik DC Comics. “Bisa membuat komik di usia setua ini, rasanya sangat menyenangkan namun sedikit menakutkan,” aku Bourdain saat memperkenalkan Get Jiro di San Diego Comic Con 2012.</span></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48209\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48209\" data-attachment-id=\"48209\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anthony-bourdain-dan-komik/attachment/03-anthony-bourdain/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-anthony-bourdain\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-anthony-bourdain-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48209\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Eater\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-anthony-bourdain.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-anthony-bourdain-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48209\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Eater</p></div></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Komik ini menceritakan tentang sosok koki sushi bernama Jiro-san yang memukau masyarakat lewat masakannya. Dalam dunia Get Jiro, makanan adalah </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">serious business</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> dan para koki membentuk kubu layaknya organisasi mafia. Jiro menemukan dirinya terjebak dalam konflik kelompok-kelompok ini. Ia dipaksa bergabung ke dalam organisasi tersebut, dan jika menolak ia akan mati.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dalam Get Jiro, kamu bisa menemukan obsesi dan </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">passion</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> dari Bourdain menyatu dengan kemampuan penulisannya yang </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">witty</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> dan punya humor unik. Dalam satu adegan diceritakan ada dua geng masak yang sedang bertarung. Jiro-san yang merasa kesal, dengan santainya memotong lengan seorang anggota geng menggunakan pisau. Alih-alih marah, para anggota geng justru terkesima dengan kemampuan Jiro-san memainkan pisaunya.</span></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48210\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48210\" data-attachment-id=\"48210\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anthony-bourdain-dan-komik/attachment/04-anthony-bourdain/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-anthony-bourdain\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-anthony-bourdain-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48210\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Comic Books World\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-anthony-bourdain.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-anthony-bourdain-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48210\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Comic Books World</p></div></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Karir Bourdain dalam dunia komik berlanjut lewat sekuel berjudul Get Jiro: Blood and Sushi di tahun 2015. Bahkan di tahun 2018 ini ia baru saja memulai </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">mini-series</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> sepanjang empat episode dengan judul <a href=\"https://www.darkhorse.com/Books/3000-827/Anthony-Bourdains-Hungry-Ghosts-HC\">Hungry Ghosts</a>. Kali ini menggandeng ilustrator Alberto Ponticelli dan Vanesa Del Rey, komik terbitan Dark Horse ini juga masih mengusung gaya penceritaan Bourdain yang </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">witty</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, namun juga menggugah selera berkat obsesi kulinernya.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dengan meninggalnya Bourdain, mungkin kita tak bisa melihat lagi kejeniusan dari kisah Get Jiro maupun Hungry Ghosts. Bahkan jika sang </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">co-writer </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Joel Rose mencoba membuat komik bertema kuliner baru, tanpa Bourdain semuanya tak akan pernah lagi sama. Selamat jalan, Anthony Bourdain. </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Write in peace.</span></i></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48211\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48211\" data-attachment-id=\"48211\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anthony-bourdain-dan-komik/attachment/05-anthony-bourdain/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-anthony-bourdain\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-anthony-bourdain-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48211\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-anthony-bourdain.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: The Daily Beast\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-anthony-bourdain.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-anthony-bourdain-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48211\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: The Daily Beast</p></div></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Apakah kamu juga sama-sama menyukai dunia komik dan penulisan seperti Anthony Bourdain? Bagaimana awal cerita kamu mengenal dan mencintai komik dan penulisan? Apakah mereka menjadi </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">first love</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> kamu, sebagaimana Bourdain menjadikan komik </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">first love-</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">nya? Jangan malu untuk berbagi cerita kamu di kolom komentar.</span></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"58594924-f915-5f4d-83e8-c17eaf1ca402"}}}